# Smart amplifier playback Pipeline
#
#  Playback with smart_amp(Smart Amplifier), it will take the feedback(B2) from capture pipeline.
#
# Pipeline Endpoints for connection are :-
#
#	Playback smart_amp
#	B1 (DAI buffer)
#
#
#  host PCM_P -- B0 --> smart_amp -- B1--> sink DAI0
#			   ^
#			   |
#			   B2
#			   |

